title: 469.167 BORDER CITY ENTERPRISE ZONE; DURATION.
text:
MS 2011 Supp [Repealed, 2012 c 294 art 2 s 43]
The designation of a border city enterprise zone is effective until terminated by resolution adopted by the city in which the border city enterprise zone is located.
MS 2011 Supp [Repealed, 2012 c 294 art 2 s 43]
